@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v0 + (wp.abs(tmp + 0.75) / wp.abs(v1 + 0.97)))
    tmp = wp.abs((0.25 + wp.abs(v2 + 0.38)))
    v0 = 0.68
    v0 = v0
    tmp = (0.09 * ((tmp + 0.86 + v0 + 0.38) / (v1 + 0.35 + v2 + 0.03)))
    v0 = wp.sin((0.74 * tmp))
    v1 = (0.83 + tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
